  <description>
    <p>Tauon Music Box is a music player for playback of audio files. Designed to be streamlined but powerful while putting the user in control of their music collection.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple drag and drop file importing</li>
      <li>Built in CUE sheet detection</li>
      <li>Groups tracks by folder</li>
      <li>Easily create and manage playlists</li>
      <li>Quick and powerful searching</li>
      <li>Scrobble and love tracks to last.fm</li>
      <li>Large album art and gallery layouts avaliable</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

